config SCHED_ARG
	bool "ARG Scheduler Hook Infrastructure"
	depends on SMP
	depends on ARM64 || COMPILE_TEST
	default n
	help
	  Lightweight hook layer for the ARG (Advanced Resource Governor)
	  scheduler module. Contains zero scheduling policy.

	  Inserts 5 hook points in CFS core path:
	    enqueue_task, ttwu_do_activate, pick_next_task,
	    calc_global_load_tick, enqueue_task_rt.

	  Each hook adds 1 load-acquire + 1 predictable branch when
	  the ARG module is not loaded. Required by CONFIG_SCHED_ARG_KMM.
	  If unsure, say N.

config SCHED_MC
